      "value": "<p>&gt;@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.YMGOKoZtKgJqIsAD]{Mechanic Trick}</p>\n<p>When you activate your energy shield, choose two of the following damage types: cold, electricity, or fire. While your shield is active, you gain resistance to the chosen damage types equal to [[floor(@classes.mechanic.levels/2)]]{half your mechanic level}. You must have the @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.xcIBsW8VL3DD9rVU]{Energy Shield (Ex)} mechanic trick to learn this trick.</p>\n<p><em>Edit the Modifiers to select the correct resistance types. Defaults to Cold and Fire</em></p>"
